memories records travelers warden judgment~
The Warden's records are extensive and methodical. Every traveler


is assessed on their navigation method, their adaptability, their


treatment of other travelers they encountered, and their emotional


state under pressure. The records note patterns across centuries:


the most successful navigators are consistently characterized by


patience, observation, and a willingness to admit when they are wrong.


~
